snippet.title: Guimo gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Guimo, PC game produced by Cia do Software in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/guimo/7688/
Playing a quick introduction of the first level of this platform arcade game.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Alien Carnage - https://youtu.be/mCl-fJIa6_E
Pitfall - https://youtu.be/JlSighUAZ6I
Iron Blood - https://youtu.be/gm-spPIfhHk
